  ScenarioTitle: Feeling Followed
  Description: You notice a group of people keeping pace behind you. They seem to
    be following you.
  ChoiceAText: Go to a lit shop
  FeedbackA: Smart move! Entering a public, well-lit place with other people is the
    best way to deter followers.
  IsSafeA: 1
  ChoiceBText: Take a shortcut
  FeedbackB: Risky! Taking dark shortcuts or alleys makes you more vulnerable. Stay
    on main roads.
